```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as 用户
    participant FE as 前端 /login
    participant GW as gateway
    participant DB as users / sessions
    participant RD as Redis (黑名单)
    participant POL as 公安接口

    U->>FE: 输入手机号 + 密码
    FE->>GW: POST /auth/login

    GW->>DB: GetUserByPhone
    DB-->>GW: user (含 password_hash)
    GW->>GW: bcrypt.Verify → 通过
    GW->>GW: auth.Issue(JWT 双 token)
    GW->>DB: INSERT sessions (refresh hash)
    GW->>DB: TouchUserLogin
    GW-->>FE: 200 {accessToken, refreshToken, user}

    Note over FE,GW: 后续请求带 Authorization: Bearer <access>

    alt 高危操作（如修改风控等级）
        FE->>GW: PUT /risk-level/state
        GW->>GW: Auth middleware 验签
        GW->>RD: 查 jti 是否被吊销
        RD-->>GW: not revoked
        GW->>GW: RBAC RequireRole("family_admin")
        GW-->>FE: 200
    end

    alt access 过期
        FE->>GW: any request
        GW-->>FE: 401 AUTH_TOKEN_EXPIRED
        FE->>GW: POST /auth/refresh (refreshToken)
        GW->>DB: 校验 sessions.revoked = false
        GW-->>FE: 200 {new access}
    end

    alt 注销
        U->>FE: 点退出
        FE->>GW: POST /auth/logout
        GW->>DB: UPDATE sessions SET revoked = true
        GW->>RD: SADD jwt:revoked <jti> EX <ttl>
        GW-->>FE: 200
    end
```
